Package: tidyhwsd
Type: Package
Title: Tidy Interface to HWSD v2.0 Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Your",
           family = "Name",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "you@example.com")
  )
Description: Provides a tidyverse-friendly interface to the Harmonized World Soil
    Database (HWSD) v2.0. Includes helpers to download the HWSD v2.0 index grid,
    extract point or gridded attributes, list available properties, and plot
    rasters with ggplot2 while keeping terra objects for performance.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2)
Imports:
    terra,
    sf,
    cli,
    dplyr,
    tibble,
    rlang,
    httr
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Config/testthat/edition: 3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
